      "side": 1,
      "message": "Love the simplification.\n\nI did a lot of the complicating sk4f / scale-translate special casing, was was certainly profiling as I did it. That said, we can land.and.hope that we don\u0027t slow down in a meaningful way.\n\nSomewhat separate: have we tried just removing quickReject as a feature? Wonder what gets:\n- slower\n- faster\n- wrong\n?\n",
      "revId": "7a43ac779bb1940614b0a40982437e787d662a0c",
